item.title: 【Helpdesk】[OFFERING] I can convert 360RA MPEG-3D files to .wav for you
item.description:
I see a lot of people asking how to convert MHA1/MPEG-3D files into playable .wav files. I have coded a tool for it and I will happily convert them for you whenever I have time.


What you need to do if you want me to convert your MHA1/MPEG-3D files:

Send me a DM on ShareMania with the files you want me to convert to a host, (Google Drive, Pixeldrain, MEGA and MediaFire preferred) and I will send the converted .wav files back to you.
